<html>
<head>
<meta charset='UTF-8'>
<script type='text/javascript'
        src='//code.jquery.com/jquery-1.8.3.js'></script>
<link rel="stylesheet"
      href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.3/css/bootstrap.min.css">
<script src="https://netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.0.3/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<link rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-datepicker/1.5.0/css/bootstrap-datepicker3.min.css">
<script type='text/javascript'
        src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap-datepicker/1.5.0/js/bootstrap-datepicker.min.js"></script>
<script type='text/javascript'>
\$(function(){
    \$('.input-group.date').datepicker({
        calendarWeeks: true,
        todayHighlight: true,
        autoclose: true,
        startDate: '$startDate',
        endDate: '$endDate',
        datesDisabled: [ $disabled ],
    });
});
</script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/cgi.css">
</head>
<body>
<!--
see this site:
https://www.jquery-az.com/bootstrap-datepicker-set-up-guide-with-8-online-demos-and-code/
-->
<img src='/static/images/mmc-teal.png' width=200>
<p>
<h1>Mountain Experience Registration</h1>
The cost for the day is \$${ME_cost}.
<br>
Available only on ${weekdays}, some Sundays, and select weekdays.
<br>
Reservations must be made at least 24 hours in advance.
<p>
Mountain Experience bookings cannot be made
more than 90 days in advance.
[% IF noME.0 %]
    Due to other onsite programming, the following dates
    are not available for Mountain Experience bookings:
    <p>
    <ul>
    [% FOR d IN noME %]
        <li>$d</li>
    [% END %]
    </ul>
[% END %]
<form name=form action=reg1 method=get>
<input type=hidden name=id value=0>
<input type=hidden name=dir value=pr>
<input type=hidden name=mountain_experience value=1>
<p style="margin-top: .2in">
<table cellpadding=5>
<tr>
<th>Date</th>
<td>
<span class="input-group date">
  <input type="text" class="form-control" name=arr_date>
  <span class="input-group-addon">
  <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-calendar"></i>
  </span>
</span>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p style="margin-top: .2in">
Which meals would you like?
<ul>
<label><input type=checkbox id=lunch name=lunch value='yes'>
Lunch (12:30-1:30 pm weekdays); Brunch (10:00-11:00 am) Saturdays</label><br>
<label><input type=checkbox id=dinner name=dinner value='yes'>
Dinner (5:15-6:15 pm)</label><br>
</ul>
<p>
Which of these activities would you like?
<ul>
<label><input type=checkbox id=yoga_class name=yoga_class value='1'>
Yoga Class (3:30-4:45 pm)</label><br>
<label><input type=checkbox id=guided_hike name=guided_hike value='1'>
Guided Walk (11:30 am-12:30 pm)</label><br>
</ul>
<p>
If you are bringing children enter their names and ages here:<br>
<input type=text size=30 name=children_name_age>
<span style="color: #aaaaaa">&nbsp;For example: Nandini 5, Elliott 8</span><br>
Children 4 years and under are welcome free of charge;<br>
for 5-12 years old, fees are discounted 50%.<br>
Older children should be registered separately.
<p>
<button type="submit">Submit</button>
</form>
</body>
</html>
